{"ec":"ET00007422","t":"Kanchana","img":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/thumbnail/large/kanchana-et00007422-1769579671.jpg","og":"https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/movies/images/mobile/listing/xxlarge/kanchana-et00007422-1769579671.jpg","d":"Raghava is a typical jobless youth who spends his day playing cricket with his friends and beating up antisocial elements. However, he suffers from an irrational fear of ghosts, and retreats to the safety of his home after sunset. So great is his fear, that he prefers to sleep with his mother and have her accompany him to the bathroom at night. This creates major annoyance in the household, which is also populated by Raghava`s brother, sister-in-law and their children.","rd":"2011-07-15","rt":165,"ct":"UA","g":["Drama"],"l":["Tamil","Telugu"],"f":["2D"],"i":null,"cast":[["Raghavendra Lawrence","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/raghavendra-lawrence-5258-1664524558.jpg"],["R. Sarathkumar","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/r-sarathkumar-33822-1778494730.jpg"],["Raai Laxmi","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/raai-laxmi-1251-04-05-2020-04-20-41.jpg"],["Kovai Sarala","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/kovai-sarala-9382-1686290181.jpg"],["Devadarshini","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/devadarshini-chetan-24847-1736851935.jpg"]],"crew":{"d":[["Raghavendra Lawrence","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/raghavendra-lawrence-5258-1664524558.jpg"]],"p":[],"m":[["S. Thaman","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/s.-thaman-26860-24-03-2017-17-34-18.jpg"]],"c":[["Vetri","https://assets-in.bmscdn.com/iedb/artist/images/website/poster/large/vetri-iein013690-24-03-2017-15-30-38.jpg"]],"e":[]}}
